Write a  program to copy a string from one variable to other using string library functions:

Input Format:

Input consist of 1 string.
Sample Input & Output:

hello

The copied String is hello.

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        //creating an object for scanner class
        Scanner sc= new Scanner(System.in);
        
        //initializing the variables for user input
        String input = sc.nextLine();
        System.out.print("The copied String is "+input);
    }
}
